{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──3个月后。\n整体院继续顺利经营着。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "然而，大部分收入都花在商店购物上了...",
      "playSE": "shop_door"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_smile_01",
      "text": "客人，今天也欢迎光临♡",
      "characterImage": "clerk/clerk.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(又来了...今天买什么好呢...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_pleased_01",
      "text": "客人的累计购买金额终于超过500万日元了♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "五、500万!? 花了那么多吗..."
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_smile_01",
      "text": "呵呵♡ 真了不起♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_pleased_01",
      "text": "其实...我有个请求想拜托客人♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "请、请求？"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_pleased_01",
      "text": "可以让我用客人来测试正在开发的试制品吗?♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "当然，会做比VIP服务更刺激的事情...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──从那以后，{{playerName}}成了店员的实验对象。"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_smile_01",
      "text": "今天是新型催情油♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_pleased_01",
      "text": "据说涂抹的瞬间全身就会变成敏感带...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "首先我先涂在自己身上，然后再给客人涂♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "店员开始脱衣服，往全身涂抹油。"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "嗯...♡ 太厉害了...全身真的变得敏感了...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "胸部也要涂满...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "嗯...♡ 乳头...变得硬邦邦的了♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "小穴也要...啊啊♡ 阴蒂...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(好、好厉害的景象...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_pleased_01",
      "text": "那么，客人...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "我用胸部给您涂油♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "店员把自己的胸部紧贴在{{playerName}}的身体上，涂抹着油。"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "看...能感觉到我的乳头变硬了吗?♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "哇啊啊啊! 太厉害了! 全身都...!"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "下半身...用小穴给您涂♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "店员跨坐在{{playerName}}身上，一边摩擦湿润的私处一边涂油。"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "啊啊♡ 我的爱液和油在客人的鸡巴上...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "呜呜!"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_pleased_01",
      "text": "呵呵♡ 反应也很好♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_smile_01",
      "text": "数据也收集好了，这样应该可以商品化了♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──另一天"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_pleased_01",
      "text": "今天是电动式新型器具...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "请让我装在客人的鸡巴上收集数据♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(现在什么都来吧...!)"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "{{playerName}}已经完全成了店员的实验对象。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "然而，他对能比任何人都早体验刺激的新产品\n感到一种奇妙的满足感。"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_pleased_01",
      "text": "多亏了客人，我们不断开发出优秀的产品♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_smile_01",
      "text": "今后也请长久地...当我的测试员...♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "店员",
      "expression": "face_horny_01",
      "text": "下次会准备更厉害的♡"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "好! 我很期待!"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "本应作为整体师成功的，\n却不知不觉成了成人用品的实验对象。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "但这或许也是一种幸福。",
      "triggerEnding": "shop"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "【SHOP END - 店员的测试员END】",
      "triggerEnding": "shop"
    }
  ]
}